-- Menacorp of Abu Dhabi Hires Rantisi as Head of Brokerage
-- B y   Z a h r a   H a n k i r
-- 2012-08-06T04:00:00Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-08-06/menacorp-of-abu-dhabi-hires-rantisi-as-head-of-brokerage.html
Menacorp , an Abu Dhabi-based
financial services company, hired Nabil Rantisi as managing
director of brokerage, group Chief Executive Officer Fathi Ben
Grira said.  Rantisi, 35, “shall play an important role with respect to
the development of our services toward institutional investors
both locally and internationally,” Ben Grira said in an e-mail
to Bloomberg News. Mena Corp Financial Services LLC was ranked
third among 51 brokerages by value traded on the  Dubai Financial
Market  in July, according to bourse data.  Rantisi previously served as the director of regional
brokerage at Rasmala Investment Bank Ltd. He confirmed the
Menacorp appointment when contacted by Bloomberg News.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Zahra Hankir in Dubai at 
 zhankir@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
